The outstandingly bright Lumo LED 18 Ceilinglite Caravan Light combines the double benefits of an extremely long lifespan with impressively low power consumption and is an ideal light for caravans, motorhomes campervans, and boats.

Product Name: Bonus electrical PMS 3H Power Management System (Horizontal)
Product Description:
Bonus Electrical PMS 3H (Horizontal) Control Panel

The Bonus PMS3 is specifically designed for conversions where the user is looking for a simple system to perform basic tasks, whilst charging your leisure battery and fuse protecting your 12v appliances, such as powering your campervans fridge and lighting.

Using the Bonus PMS3 power management system, you are able to safely power both 12v and 230v equipment installed in your campervan or motorhome. The Bonus PMS3 also features 4 fused outputs, a battery voltage indicator, and a separate switch for the water pump.

RCD and MCB Protected.

The Bonus PMS3 Campervan motorhome power management system comes complete with a Residual Current Device (RCD) which will monitor the system, and close down the unit in case of current fluctuations deemed detrimental. Two miniature circuit breakers (MCB’s) are also installed, they are designed to protect the system against overloads and short circuits.

Reverse Polarity Detection

The PMS3 has reverse polarity detection in case of sire mains being incompatible with the polarity in your campervan or motorhome.

PMS3 Power Management System features:

  • 13.8 Volt DC : Fully Stabilised Power Supply/Battery Charger WITH short circuit and over current protection. Constant current limit at 12A.
  • Mains 230 Volt AC: Earth leakage protection; (RCB and MCB protection)
  • 18 amp 240v battery charger
  • 4 Fused outputs
  • battery condition meter
  • battery change over switch
  • pump isolation switch

Dimensions:

  • Unit: 258mm W x 130mm H x 175mm D
  • Faceplate: 285mm W x 155mm H

Puky Ceety Cat S6 2-in-1 Tricycle & Pushchair

The Puky Ceety C6 brings you a trike and pushchair all in one!

The Puky Ceety Cat S6 2 in 1 Kid's Tricycle & Pushchair features a comfort which offers a variety of functions and equipment and is fun for parents and children (up to the age of four)! When at home the carrier bag can be taken off the Ceety C6 Kid's Tricycle easily so that little things can be carried inside quickly.

Children sit extremely comfortably and safely on the Puky Cat S6 Ceety Tricycle & Pushchair because the ergonomics are optimally adjusted for young passengers and parents will find pushing the Ceety tricycle a pleasure thanks to the ergonomic Vario comfort guide pole offering the same comfort as other high quality pushchairs, so that both parent and child can be comfortable and happy together!

Osprey Mountainboard ATB Off Road Dirtboard

For thrill seekers bored with simply cruising the streets on their basic skateboards, the Osprey Mountainboard ATB Off Road Dirtboard is the perfect upgrade! Osprey Mountainboard ATB Off Road Dirtboard features include:

Product Description:
Bowman Swimming Pool Heat Exchangers

Available in Cupro Nickel, Titanium and Stainless Steel, Bowman Swimming Pool Heat Exchangers are a cost and energy efficient heating solution for your swimming pool.

Easy to maintain, energy efficient and cost effective

Available in a range of materials which make them suitable for all types of pool set up, these Bowman Swimming Pool Heat Exchangers also incorporate a higher volume of heat transfer tubes than most heat exchangers so that your pool can be heated quicker and dramatically reduce fuel costs in the process!

Please note that as for all metal fittings within a pool system the water chemistry must be balanced (especially pH) to avoid chemical damage.

If you have a salt chlorination system in the pool you need to use a Titanium heat exchanger.

Easy to maintain and install

The Bowman Swimming Pool Heat Exchangers have removable end covers and tube stacks providing handy cleaning access, whilst the 5113 and 5114 units come complete with imperial and metric solvent weld adaptors for easy installation into the pipe work of your swimming pool.

Please note: The best selling of our Bowman Heat Exchangers is the Cupro Nickel 5113-3C, and we generally recommend this unit to most of our customers due to it fitting all the basic requirements of the average swimming pool. The 5113-3C is supplied with both 1.5 inch ABS pipe connectors & 50mm pipe connections.

Product Name: Dometic Under Bench Air Conditioner Vents
Product Description:
Venting for Dometic Under Bench Air Conditioners

It is not advisable to use the same air ducting from any blown air heating system already fitted. Usually warm air outlets are low down to allow the warmed air to rise, Chilled air is at it's most effective when falling downwards. An outlet suitable for terminating each duct is available, as well as a square and a round exterior grill to allow the airflow into and out of the unit itself underneath the leisure vehicle. The 90 degree bends allow very tight corners to be achieved in wardrobes and cupboards etc.

Fittings Available

  • 190mm Round Inlet Vents
  • Rectangular Inlet Vent
  • 90 Degree Elbow
  • Blown Air Heater End
  • Blown Air End Grill

Please see Truma ducting fittings in the related products column

Product Description:
Mercury Professional Soft Start Compact Inverter (600W)

Using a modified sine wave to power mains equipment from either 12 or 24v battery, the ultra efficient Mercury Professional Soft Start Compact Inverter (600W) is ideal used as a back up during power cuts or for a handy power supply whilst travelling.

Ideal for use with TVs, hand held tools, computers and other electrical appliances (particularly in caravans and motorhomes!) the Mercury Professional Soft Start Compact Inverter (600W) provides a stabilised 240v mains output voltage with short-circuit, soft start circuitry to protect equipment on start up as well as overload protection.  

Mercury Professional Soft Start Compact Inverter (600W) features

  • Soft start (Minimises inverter shutdown when using large inductive loads)
  • Reverse polarity protection
  • Battery low/high shutdown
  • Short circuit and overload protection
  • Over temperature protection
  • Modified sine wave output
  • LED fault indicator

Please note: The 600W Mercury Soft Start Compact Inverter comes with crocodile clips for connection, not a cigarette lighter style plug. For a hard wired compact inverter please see the 1000W Compact Inverter.

Hyundai HYT80 Trash Debris Flood Emergency Water Pump

Portable and lightweight yet hard wearing, the rugged Hyundai HYT80 Debris Flood Emergency Water Pump is designed to cope with suspended particles and debris (of up to 35mm in size) and is powered by the robust Hyundai 6.5hp IC210 petrol engine, meaning it can cope with the tough demands of water flow and blockages easily!

The Hyundai HYT80 Trash Flood Emergency Water Pump is easy to store due to its clever, compact design, and because there’s no electrical supply required is a safer all-round water pump with no risk of electrocution which also allows freedom for you to use this trash pump in remote or rural areas without having to worry about finding a source of electricity.

Hyundai HT80 Trash Debris Flood Emergency Water Pump features

  • Petrol Water Debris Pump
  • Ideal for domestic use, drainage, gardens, boats, irrigation and flood emergencies.
  • Very Impressive Maximum Flow Rate of 600 Litres Per Minute
  • Portable and Lightweight
  • Can draw from a height of up to 6m (if bled fully first)
  • Impressive maximum flow rate of up to 53,000 litres per hour!

Please note: The HYT80 is essentially a fresh water pump and is not suitable for use with seawater or other chemicals as this may cause damage to its internal components.

Product Name: Hyundai DHYC50LE Diesel Chemical Water Pump
Product Description:
Hyundai DHYC50LE Diesel Chemical Water Pump

Powered by the Hyundai 6hp OHV 4-stroke diesel engine, with electric start and its own 12v battery, the Hyundai DHYC50LE Diesel Chemical Water Pump is a heavy duty, easy to start machine suitable for liquid fertiliser, seawater or other similar corrosive chemicals!

With a corrosion resistant plastic body and an impressively powerful flow rate of 500 litres a minute, the Hyundai DHYC50LE Diesel Chemical Water Pump takes less time to get the job done compared to petrol pumps of a smaller horsepower and is also more economical to run as it uses red diesel (commonly found on farms or fishing boats).

Hyundai DHYC50LE Diesel Chemical Water Pump features

  • Diesel-driven water pump with a 50mm inlet/outlet (2" bore approx.)
  • Capable of pumping up to 32,000 litres per hour (533L per min)
  • Tough plastic pump, specifically for pumping corrosive liquids, chemicals, liquid fertilizer or sea water
  • 6hp four stroke diesel electric key start engine
  • Maximum pumping head of 26m and lift of 7m

Product Description:
Laars Jandy Zodiac Legacy LRZ Swimming Pool Gas Heater Boiler

A fantastic long term investment for swimming pool owners, the Laars Jandy Zodiac Legacy LRZ Gas Boiler Heater is an efficient pool heating solution with dependable high performance and user friendly features which put you in complete control of operations and the temperature of your swimming pool.

Compact and lightweight with an energy efficient design featuring a copper heat exchanger, stainless steel corrosion resistant burners and Flo-Thru™ baffles the Laars Jandy Zodiac Legacy LRZ Gas Heater Boiler delivers an impressively efficient heat transfer and has been time and again proven as a reliable, high quality and enduring swimming pool heating system.

Laars Jandy Zodiac Legacy LRZ Swimming Pool Gas Heater features include

  • The Zodiac Legacy LRZ Swimming Pool boiler is suitable for both indoor or outdoor use
  • No electrical connection required (Millivolt operation)
  • Copper heat exchanger and Flo-Thru™ baffles for an efficient heat transfer
  • The Zodiac Legacy LRZ with stainless steel corrosion resistant burners
  • Ceramic fibre combustion chamber for a lightweight and compact design

Product Description:
Certikin BTU S/S heat exchanger & Stat kit

The Certikin S/S Heat Exchanger & Stat Kit available in different levels of heat exchange settings to suit your needs. Including 100,000 BTU, 130,000 BTU, 170,000 BTU, 230,000 BTU & 460,000 BTU Heat Exchanger Kits. Achieve optimal heating efficiency for your swimming pool, Koi pond, or solar heating system with the Certikin S/S Heat Exchanger & Stat Kit. Designed for seamless integration with standard boilers, this high-performance heat exchanger transfers heat efficiently from your home’s heating system to your pool, ensuring the perfect water temperature whenever you need it.

Key Features:

  • Versatile Heat Exchange Options: Available in a range of BTU settings—100,000, 130,000, 170,000, 230,000, and 460,000—so you can select the model that best suits your pool capacity and boiler output.
  • Durable Stainless Steel Construction: Built from high-quality stainless steel, this heat exchanger offers long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance. Its compact design also saves space when wall-mounted.
  • Temperature Control: Equipped with a thermostat pocket at the top of the unit, the heat exchanger allows easy insertion of a thermostat probe to monitor and maintain your desired pool temperature. For greater flexibility, an additional stainless steel pocket can be installed in the pool return line (thermostat and pocket sold separately; we recommend the Certikin Digital Thermostat).
  • Easy Installation: Designed with 1.5" female thread composite unions (or 2" for the 460,000 BTU model), installation is straightforward. The kit includes everything you need: a heat exchanger, Honeywell thermostat, stat pocket, drilled and threaded end cap, and composite unions.

Whether you're looking to maintain a comfortable temperature in your pool or enhance your solar heating system, the Certikin S/S Heat Exchanger & Stat Kit offers a reliable and efficient solution for your heating needs.

Please Note:

  • Choose Size Accordingly: Your heat exchanger should be sized according to your swimming pool capacity, situation and boiler output. The stainless steel heat exchangers are manufactured in 100, 130, 170, 230 and 460 thousand B.T.U. maximum output.
  • Installation: 1.5" Female thread composite unions are required to install this heat exchanger – 11/2” for HESPA, HE100, HE130, HE170 & HE230. 2” unions are required for the HE460.
  • Each kit includes: Heat Exchanger, Honeywell Stat, Stat Pocket, Drilled and Threaded End Cap & 1.5” Comp Unions 100-230 2” 460
  • Not Suitable for Saltwater Pools: Please note that these heat exchangers are not designed for use with saltwater pools.

Product Name: Elecro Vulcan 3kw Nano Above Ground Titanium Swimming Pool Heater
Product Description:
Elecro Vulcan 3 KW Nano Splasher Plug & Play Electric Pool Heater (All Titanium)

Made in England, using the latest technology and materials of the highest quality, the Nano Splasher Plug & Play Electric Pool Heater (titanium) is ideal for above ground swimming pools.

Easy to install

Built for longevity, the Elecro Nano Splasher Plug & Play Electric Pool Heater (titanium) is a 3kW unit which can be plugged straight into a plug socket and features a reliable flow switch to safely shut down the heater in the event that water flow isn’t detected.

Easy to Plumb to your Swimming Pool Pipe Work

Plumbing of the Elecro Nano Splasher Plug & Play Electric Pool Heater (Titanium) to your swimming pool is easy. Supplied with adaptors to push fit a 1.5 inch or 1.25 inch flexible pipe, the Elecro Nano Splasher Plug & Play Electric Heater (Titanium) also has a 1.5 inch BSP female thread to join on to standard pool pipe work. For pools with Salt Chlorinators this heater is suitable.

Before you buy, answer these simple (might seem dumb) questions.

  1. Does your pool have a pump? You can’t have a heater without one
  2. Are you going to plug the heater into an extension lead?  Most people are, make sure it’s a heavy duty extension lead not some flimsy lead you might use on say an electric lawnmower for example.  Using a lightweight extension lead will result in the socket on the lead overheating and even melting causing the heater plug to overheat and become damaged as well.
  3. Are you planning on using the heater on a hydrotherapy pool for animals (dogs or cats for example).  If so this voids warranty, even with filters animal hairs can damage the flow switch and other parts.
  4. Do you have an Intex pool that has the threaded nut type connection, if so you'll have a problem connecting the heater, check with you Intex pool supplier to see if they have a connection kit.
  5. This heater is only suitable for pool sizes of 10ft and 12ft.

For more information see the video below

This video shows the old version which we've left here as a lot of the features are the same.

 

Elecro Nano Splasher Plug & Play Electric Pool Heater (Titanium) features

  • Robust, durable construction
  • Easy installation, fully equipped and pre-wired
  • Fully equipped
  • Easy to install
  • Ultra-reliable flow switch allowing for safe operation as low as 1m³/hour
  • Incoloy 825 heating element
  • 316 Stainless Steel flow tube
  • Control thermostat 0-40°C (1°C differential)
  • Safety thermal cut out 60°C (manual reset)
  • Supplied with hose tails for connections to 1¼" or 1½" flexible pipe
  • Compact, durable design
  • Titanium flow tube and titanium heating element
  • Can be floor or vertically wall mounted
  • Vortex, long life, stay clean heating element technology
  • 100% efficiency throughout the product life
  • Silent operation

Product Name: Elecro Evolution Swimming Pool Heater Titanium 4.5kW to 25kW
Product Description:
Electro Evolution Swimming Pool Heater Titanium

The Electro Evolution 2 Swimming Pool Heater is designed to deliver reliable, efficient heating for pools, spas, and ponds. Built with high-quality titanium components, this powerful unit provides maximum efficiency, optimal performance and a long lifespan. The Evolution 2 provides dependable temperature control to suit your needs, whether you're heating an koi pond, indoor pool or spa, this is the right heater for you! Even in cold UK weather condition, this heater still works its magic! This heater can be mounted to floors and walls, making it versatile and easy to install. The Electro Evolution 2 is an ideal heater, which works best providing backup heat in conjunction with heat pumps or serving as the primary heat source. To ensure that your pool or spa is always at the perfect temperature, get your Electro Evolution 2 Swimming Pool Heater today!

Key Features:

  • Maximum Efficiency: Provides maximum energy use throughout the heater's life.
  • Robust Construction: Made with titanium heating elements and flow tubes for durability and longevity.
  • Versatile Mounting: Can be wall or floor-mounted for flexible installation.
  • Safety Features: Includes a gold-tipped reed flow switch and over-temperature protection with a manual reset.
  • Silent Operation: Quietly heats water without disruption.
  • Vortex Technology: The long-life, stay-clean heating element ensures minimal maintenance.
  • Wide Power Range: Available in power outputs from 1kW to 24kW.
  • Simple Control: Analogue thermostat with a 1.2°C differential or digital control for more precise settings.

Before you buy, answer these simple (might seem dumb) questions.

  1. Does your pool have a pump? You can’t have a heater without one
  2. Are you going to plug the heater into an extension lead?  Most people are, make sure it’s a heavy duty extension lead not some flimsy lead you might use on say an electric lawnmower for example.  Using a lightweight extension lead will result in the socket on the lead overheating and even melting causing the heater plug to overheat and become damaged as well.
  3. Are you planning on using the heater on a hydrotherapy pool for animals (dogs or cats for example).  If so this voids warranty, even with filters animal hairs can damage the flow switch and other parts.
  4. Do you have an Intex pool that has the threaded nut type connection, if so you'll have a problem connecting the heater, check with you Intex pool supplier to see if they have a connection kit.

Product Name: Calorex I-PAC (X-Range) Swimming Pool Side Outlet Extended Season Heat Pump
Option Set: Calorex I-Pac X Range Heat Pump
Product Description:
Calorex I-PAC X-Range Side Outlet Heat Pump

The Calorex I-PAC X-Range Side Outlet Heat Pump offers state-of-the-art Inverter technology for precise and energy-efficient pool heating. Perfect for outdoor and private pools, spa pools, and wellness centers, this heat pump ensures comfortable swimming during the extended UK pool season, operating in air temperatures as low as -5°C. Ideal for UK swimming pools and wellness centers, the Calorex I-PAC X-Range offers premium heating performance with minimal environmental impact.

Key Features:

  • Inverter Technology: Automatically adjusts the heat output based on demand, significantly reducing energy consumption and operational costs. This ensures quieter operation, with a noise reduction of up to 11 dB(A) compared to traditional on/off pumps.
  • Eco-Friendly Refrigerant: Uses R32 refrigerant with a low Global Warming Potential (GWP) of 675, making it environmentally responsible.
  • Compact & Efficient: The I-PAC X-Range is 27-46% smaller than standard heat pumps, with power ratings from 8 to 25 kW, ideal for a variety of pool sizes.
  • Whisper Mode: Reduces sound levels to near-silent operation, enhancing the experience around your pool.
  • Wi-Fi Connectivity: Built-in Wi-Fi module allows remote control via smartphone, ensuring easy adjustments from anywhere.
  • Flexible Operation: Offers multiple functions, including heating, cooling, and heat/cool mode, providing year-round comfort.
  • High Efficiency: Achieves an average COP (Coefficient of Performance) of 9.7, making it twice as efficient as conventional heat pumps.
  • Durable Build: Designed with an aluminium alloy casing and titanium condenser, ensuring long-lasting performance in the UK climate.

Featuring a smart design with 50% more thickness than traditional bubble covers the Sol+ Guard 500 Micron Geo Bubble Solar Cover is also UV stabilised which dramatically increases the lifespan of the cover as well as greatly reducing energy and chemical consumption to not only reduce your carbon footprint but also save you money in the process and increase the temperature of your swimming pool by up to 8°C.

Product Name: Calorex I-PAC+ (Y-Range) Swimming Pool Side Outlet Year Round Heat Pump
Option Set: Calorex I-Pac Y Range Heat Pump
Product Description:
Calorex I-PAC+ Y-Range Side Outlet Heat Pump

The Calorex Side Outlet Heat Pump Y Range, part of the I-PAC+ series, is the ultimate solution for year-round pool heating.  Perfect for outdoor and private pools, spa pools, and wellness centers. Powered by cutting-edge inverter technology, it optimizes energy usage by modulating its output based on the pool’s specific heating needs. Whether you’re swimming in the heat of summer or during the colder months, this heat pump operates efficiently even in air temperatures as low as -15ºC, ensuring comfortable water temperatures all year round. Whether you need rapid heating or whisper-quiet operation, the Calorex Side Outlet Heat Pump Y Range offers unmatched performance, efficiency, and durability to extend your swimming season and enhance your pool experience.

Key Features:

  • Inverter Technology: Automatically adjusts output to match pool heating demand, reducing energy consumption and running costs.
  • High Efficiency: The stepless inverter compressor delivers an average COP of 10.3, up to 2 times more efficient than traditional on/off heat pumps.
  • All-Weather Operation: Functions efficiently in temperatures as low as -15ºC, making it perfect for year-round swimming.
  • Eco-Friendly Refrigerant: Utilizes R32 refrigerant, with a low Global Warming Potential (GWP) of 675, for environmentally friendly operation.
  • Whisper-Quiet Performance: Reduces noise by 9-11 dB(A) compared to on/off models, with 'Whisper Mode' for quiet daily use and 'Boost Mode' for fast heat-up.
  • Wi-Fi Connectivity: Built-in Wi-Fi module allows remote control and monitoring of the heat pump for convenient operation.
  • Compact & Durable Design: Features a small footprint, compliant with permitted development rights, and durable aluminium alloy construction.
  • Multifunctional Operation: Choose from heating, cooling, or both with adjustable modes.
  • Soft Start Technology: Eliminates large power surges on startup, preventing inrush currents.

Product Name: Gardi Wooden Above Ground Timber Swimming Pool
Product Description:
Gardi Wooden Above Ground Timber Swimming Pool

With a build that combines intelligent features with a stunning design, Belgium made Gardi Wooden Above Ground Swimming Pools are manufactured by Gardival – one of the leading and most experienced timber product specialists in Europe.

A timber swimming pool with excellence at the heart of every component

All of the pumps and filtration equipment used with the Gardi Wooden Above Ground Swimming Pool is made by Pentair (the biggest pool equipment manufacturer in the World), meaning that you can depend on excellence right down to the functionality of your Gardi Swimming Pool.

Featuring patented unique dovetail joints with a conjoining stainless steel bar for an easy build and beautiful looking finish, the Gardi Wooden Above Ground Swimming Pool has a chic carved timber finish to the coping detail, making it the best looking on the market!

The Gardi Timber Above Ground Swimming Pool kit includes:

  • Wooden frame - 45mm treated grade 4 red fir.
  • One piece treated hardwood coping.
  • All stainless steel fittings.
  • Anti bacterial felt underlay.
  • 30 thou thick liner.
  • Wooden external stairs.
  • Stainless steel internal stairs.
  • sand filter complete with all hoses, connectors and sand.
  • pump.
  • Start up chemicals kit.
  • Cleaning kit (brush, vacuum head, pole, leaf net and thermometer).
  • Galvanised metal supports for elongated models.

Product Name: Splash Disabled Hoist Swimming Pool Lift
Product Description:
Splash Disabled Swimming Pool Lift Hoist

The Splash Disabled Swimming Pool Hoist is a semi-portable lifting system designed to provide easy and comfortable swimming pool access for individuals with physical disabilities.

Minimal maintenance, easy to use and designed for total comfort

Battery powered and operated by a screw driven actuator, the Splash Disabled Swimming Pool Lift Hoist features a durable system designed to ensure for a consistent operation and to minimise service problems.

Virtually maintenance free, the Splash Disabled Swimming Pool Lift Hoist has a uniquely designed seat for total user comfort and ease of transfer, a waterproof hand control which can be easily used by either the user or an attendant with the disabled swimming pool life hoist also featuring a waterproof control box and battery with a small waterproof cover included to further protect the control box when the system is out of use.

All Splash Disabled Swimming Pool Lift Hoists come with corrosion resistant components (including powder coated aluminium for the arms and housing alongside powder coated stainless steel for the mast, base and seat frame.

The Splash Disabled Swimming Pool Lift Hoist is availble in the following models:

  • Standard Pool Lift Hoist: Provides 300lb lifting capacity. Mounted to deck with standard 1.9 ID round anchor socket.
  • Spa Lift Hoist: Designed for use with spas up to 52” (132 cm) above the deck.
  • Hi / Lo Spa & Pool Lift Hoist: The perfect lift for facilities that have an above ground spa and an in-ground pool. The dual position chair allows a single lift to be used in both locations.
  • Extended Reach Pool Lift Hoist: For use with pools with unusual gutter configurations requiring a longer reach to the water line.

Product Name: Waterco Multicyclone Plus Centrifugal Swimming Pool Filter
Product Description:
Waterco Multicyclone Plus Centrifugal Swimming Pool Filter

A revolutionary way to filter your swimming pool, the Waterco MultiCyclone Plus Centrifugal Swimming Pool Filter replaces the traditional sand filter as a cheaper and easier to maintain alternative.

How does a Waterco MultiCyclone Plus Swimming Pool Filter work?

Pool water is spun through a series of cyclones in the Waterco MultiCyclone Plus Filter, whilst centrifugal force pushes the dirt into the sediment bowl (essentially, this is the same technology as a Dyson carpet cleaner except that it is adapted for water). 80% of the dirt is removed by the cyclones whilst the remaining 20% gets caught in the filter cartridge (above the sediment chamber) which leaves the water sparklingly clear.

What are the benefits of using the Waterco MultiCyclone Plus Centrifugal Swimming Pool Filter?

  • Cheaper and easier to maintain than a sand filter
  • Easy to install
  • Doesn’t require time consuming and pricey changes of sand
  • No backwashing necessary! Saving you effort as well as the thousands of litres worth of water that are required in the long run for backwashing.
  • The paper filter cartridge in the Waterco MultiCyclone Plus Centrifugal Filter only needs cleaning every month or so

There's two different base and model options available for the Waterco MultiCyclone Plus Centrifugal Pool Filter. Please use the drop down menus at the top of the page to mark your product preference prior to checkout

Product Name: Waterco MultiCyclone Pre-Filter For Swimming Pools or Koi Ponds
Product Description:
Waterco MultiCyclone Pre-Filter For Koi Ponds or Swimming Pools

Ideal for extending the lifespan of the filter in your current swimming pool or Koi pond set up, the Waterco MultiCyclone Centrifugal Pre-Filter is a revolutionary filtration system which will save you a great deal of time, money and energy!

How does a Waterco MultiCyclone Koi Pond Pre-Filter work?

Pool water gets spun through multiple hydro cyclones whilst centrifugal forces in the Waterco MultiCyclone Pre-Filter push dirt into the sediment bowl meaning that 80% of the dirt gets removed by the cyclones, leaving the remaining dirt to be caught by your existing filter for exquisitely clear water.

What are the benefits of using the Waterco MultiCyclone Swimming Pool Centrifugal Pre-Filter?

  • Cheaper and easier to maintain than a sand filter
  • Easy to install
  • Doesn’t require time consuming and pricey changes of sand
  • No backwashing necessary! Saving you effort as well as the thousands of litres worth of water that are required in the long run for backwashing.
  • No filter media to remove or clean.

There's two different model and optional Base options available for the Waterco MultiCyclone Centrifugal Pre-Filter. Please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to mark your product preference prior to checkout.

What’s the difference?

Securing the extra reach swimming pool grab rail with anchors makes for a sturdier set up with the rails connected firmly into the pool side.  It may not always be possible to install anchors leaving the flange installation version as the alternative; this means the rails are effectively held in place by 6 screws per rail.  When the choice is available the manufacturers recommend the “anchor version” grab rails.  Don't forget to tick the box if you’re going for anchors.

Product Name: Vision Plus VP 4 Digital TV Amplifier with Signal Finder
Product Description:
Vision Plus VP 4 Digital TV Amplifier with Signal Finder

Designed to be used with Vision Plus STATUS antennas (with orange logos that don’t have pullout telescopics), the Vision Plus VP4 Digital Amplifier with Signal Finder is fully wideband for television transmissions and incorporates a dedicated signal finder to locate your nearest and most powerful TV signal transmitters.

With high gain and low noise capabilities ensuring improved performance even in areas prone to poor reception, the Vision Plus VP4 Digital TV Amplifier with Signal Finder can also be used with a range of antennas that only provide a TV Output (such as Image 410, Image 420, Image 440, Image 610 and Image 620).

  • On/Off switch
  • Variable gain control
  • 2 TV outputs
  • Frequency Range UHF 470-860 Mhz
  • Amplifier Gain Max 17db
  • Gain Adjustment 15db
  • Flatness +1.5db
  • Noise Figure 2db
  • Output Impedance 75ohms

Product Name: Vision Plus 4G LTE In Line Block Interference Filter
Product Description:
Vision Plus 4G LTE In Line Block Interference Filter

The 4G Mobile Phone System (also known as LTE) has been growing in popularity since May 2013, and since then has been known in some areas to severely interfere with TV signals so dramatically that signal has been completely lost.

The straightforward and easy to install Vision Plus 4G LTE In Line Block Interference Filter prevents the 4G signal from interfering with your TV! Simply plug the Vision Plus 4G Filter into the aerial feed before it plugs into your TV amplifier, TV or set top box.

Product Name: Fiamma Motorhome Caravan Table Leg and Fixing Plates
Product Description:
Fiamma Motorhome Caravan Table Leg and Fixing Plates

This chrome plated steel table leg is perfect for use in caravans and motorhomes and can be attached into the floor of your vehicle with either a recessed or protruding plate mount depending on your preference.

What are the installation differences between the recessed & protruding plate mount options?

Should you be after a flush mounted table leg look - where the table leg is mounted seamlessly into the floor - then you will require to do a cut out into the floor as well as drill the plate into place. However, if you prefer the look which comes with a protuding plate mount then you'll require quite a bit less work as the protruding plate mount merely requires to be screwed into the floor.

Approximate Dimensions of the Motorhome Caravan Table Leg

  • Table Leg height 70cm

  • Recessed Plate cut out width: 5.5cm
  • Recessed Plate width: 15.5cm
  • Protruding Plate Width (top): 8cm
  • Protruding plate Width (bottom): 16.5cm

Please note: The Motorhome Caravan Table Leg is available either as individual spare parts or as a complete set with an option of the protruding or recessed plate mount, please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to mark your preference prior to checkout.

Product Description:
Fiamma Turbo Vent Kit

An easy and affordable way to convert the roof light of your caravan or motorhome into a fan, the 12Vdc Fiamma Turbo Vent Kit with telescopic hanging system allows for installation on all rooflights from 40x40cm (not Fiamma) to 50x70cm when the vehicle is stationary and the roof light is open. 

The Fiamma Turbo Vent Kit is composed of a ventilation system with a 24cm diameter fan and 2 telescopic hangers adjustable from 36 to 48cm.

Supplied complete with a supply cable for lighter as well as one 12Vdc power supply to allow for the rooflight to function as a fan and aspirator following electric installation in your caravan or motorhome, the Fiamma Turbo Vent Kit is also preset to work with batteries (8 x 1,5 V D not supplied).

The Fiamma Turbo Vent Kit can be installed on various rooflights including: 

  • Fiamma Vent 50

Fiamma Turbo Vent for Caravans and Motorhomes

Aerodynamic roof vent with 12v ventilation fan

A caravan and motorhome ventilation system made from high quality, shock and UV resistant materials, the Fiamma Turbo Vent consumes less energy than ventilation systems of the past and also runs peacefully quiet.

Easy electronic control

Featuring an innovative electronic circuit that allows for a hassle free, rapid change of rotation the Fiamma Turbo Vent caravan rooflight refreshes the air inside your vehicle within seconds thanks to the 12V DC variable speed motor with 10 blades. With thermostatic regulation

Equipped with Polar Control, the Fiamma Turbo Vent further regulates the ingoing and outgoing air of the fan according to the inner temperature of your caravan or motorhome, which can also save up to 50% in electricity usage.

Product Description:
700W Flatbed Caravan and Motorhome Microwave

Sleek and minimalistic microwave

This 20 Litre flatbed microwave, with easy to clean surfaces and easy cooking functions makes campsite or wild camp cooking simple and effortless. The compact design makes it ideal for smaller kitchen spaces found in caravans, campervans and motorhomes.

Perfect for mobile cooking

As the flatbed microwave does not have a turning plate, potential damage during transport is reduced and also prevents annoying rattle during your travels. The push button door release provides additional safety during use. As this is a 230V AC microwave, it requires either an electrical hookup or suitable inverter to safely power the appliance. 

700W Flatbed Microwave features

  • 20 litre microwave capacity
  • 700 watt microwave output
  • 230V AC Power Input Required
  • Green LED Display
  • Dimensions (WxHxD): 454 x 287 x 316mm

Please note: If you plan on running the Microwave through an inverter then please be aware that this requires a pure sine wave inverter only.

Product Name: Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Electronic Swimming Pool Cleaner
Product Description:
Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner

The absolute best in automatic swimming pool cleaners, the Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner is a robust robot designed for frequent use in commercial pools. The Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner provides high quality cleaning of swimming pool floors, walls and water lines and with a 30m cable length can capably service most large domestic or medium sized commercial swimming pools.  The wonder brushes are also supplied with the Dolphin Wave 100  for thorough cleaning of tiled pools.

 

Benefits of using the Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner

As well as scrubbing, brushing, vacuuming and filtering the entire pool floor, walls and waterline the Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner also uses an environmentally friendly cleaning process which disperses chemicals evenly in your swimming pool reducing the use of chlorine and other chemicals. The unique gyroscopic system delivers accurate and effective scanning for systematic cleaning across the entire pool efficiently removing algae and bacteria.

The 3 filtration options: fine, ultra fine and disposable cover all pool conditions and seasons. With an increase of 20% extra filtration capacity the Dolphin Wave 100 commercial automatic swimming pool cleaner leaves the pool water clean and free of insects, dust, hair and any other debris.

The Dolphin Wave 100 commercial swimming pool cleaner provides a plug and play fully automated user friendly cleaning solution. It is easy to use with remote control, optional program parameters and operational delay to suit every pool conditions and requirements. The Dolphin Wave 100 automatic swimming pool cleaner is supplied with a caddy for easy handling and storage.

 

Dolphin Wave 100 Commercial Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner key features

  • Cleaverclean Software
  • Thorough Brushing
  • Dual-Drive Motors
  • Swivel on Cable Prevents Tangling
  • Floor, Wall and waterline cleaning
  • Remote Control automatic operation
  • Gyroscopic Scanning System
  • 3 filtration options
  • Full Filter indicator, Operation Delay

The Dolphin Wave 100 Commerical Automatic Swimming Pool Cleaner is suitable for breach entry pools, comes with 36 months or 3000 hours warranty, includes a Wonderbrush for tiled pools and is recommended for pools of up to 25m (84ft) in length.

Product Name: Blue Lagoon Domestic UV-C Spa Swimming Pool disinfection Systems
Product Description:
Blue Lagoon Domestic UV-C Spa & Swimming Pool Disinfection Systems

The Blue Lagoon Domestic UV Spa & Swimming Pool disinfection System incorporates a high quality UV lamp as well as an electronic ballast able to withstand variable voltages to efficiently remove bacteria from your swimming pool water.

Available in four different system options with slightly different features and wattages, the Blue Lagoon Swimming Pool Sanitation System has a solution for a range of needs. To pick your preference of Blue Lagoon UV disinfection model please use the drop down menu at the top of the page prior to checkout.

Does this mean there's no need for chlorine?

No, you'll still use chlorine (or bromine) but your use of it will be reduced by as much 80% lowering all the side effects of chlorine in the process.

What does the Timer do?

This is a "count down timer" and tells you when its time to replace the lamp.  It's not an on/off timer.

What are the advantageous of using Blue Lagoon Domestic UV Spa & Swimming Pool Sanitation System?

  • UV-C light breaks down combined chlorine & protects your pool against germs
  • Provides safe & efficient disinfection of water
  • Controls against the build up of mould, bacteria & algae
  • Usage of pool cleaning chemicals (including chlorine) are reduced by up to 80%
  • Prevents against unpleasant chlorine side effects such as skin & eyes irritation and distinctive odour
  • More eco-friendly than traditional pool cleaning methods

Blue Lagoon Domestic UV Spa & Pool Sanitiser System features

  • All models come with a Philips UV-C lamp with 9000 operating hours
  • Integrated electronic pre-selector to ensure a smooth power supply
  • As a result of reflection up to 35% more UV-C yield
  • Built-in adjustable time meter for UV-C lamp
  • Digital indication for when lamp needs replacing
  • Easy installation & maintenance
  • Built from robust 316L stainless steel
  • 2 Year guarantee (*with respect to manufacturing faults)

Product Name: Rainbow Swimming Pool Bromine & Chlorine Chemical Feeder
Product Description:
Rainbow Swimming Pool Bromine & Chlorine Chemical Feeder

Saving you time and the hassle of having to manually handle swimming pool chemicals, the Rainbow Swimming Pool Chemical Feeder provide an easy to use solution for releasing chlorine & bromine whilst you can get on with other things!

Easy to install on the pressure side of the pump (downstream of the filter and heater) the Rainbow Swimming Pool Chemical Feeder allows for small Trichlor or Bromine tablets to be slowly dissolved making the sanitation of your new or swimming pool or spa incredibly easy and automatic.

Designed for permanent installation in the return line of new or existing systems, the Rainbow Swimming Pool Bromine & Chlorine Chemical Feeder features an external fine control valve which allows you to adjust the feed rate of your bromine & chlorine feeder to meet specific requirements of your pool or spa.  

Rainbow Swimming Pool Bromine & Chlorine Feeder features

  • Completely enclosed systems - no escaping fumes
  • Simple, trouble free designs with no special venting required
  • Top-loading for easy addition of chemicals
  • Available in clear amber for easy tablet viewing

 

Rainbow Swimming Pool Bromine & Chlorine Feeder Range

The in-line Model 320 feeder and freestanding Model 300 feeder both feature an external fine control valve to allow easy feed rate adjustments to meet the specific requirements for your pool or spa.

Rainbow Chemical Feeder Model 300 is ideal for retrofitting to existing pools for automatic sanitization. 

Model 320 feeder is designed for permanent installation in the return line of new or existing systems and dispenses sanitizer directly into your pool or spa.

Feeder models 3315 and 3330 provide high capacity off-line variants.

Product Description:
Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools

An affordable and high quality luxury swimming pool developed for a simpler DIY installation & complete safety, sophistication & comfort

With Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools you get to pick the features, meaning that whatever you envision your dream pool to be can easily be made a reality and at a fraction of the price and effort of a concrete swimming pool build! Choose from a range of features including comfortable integrated loungers, spa jets, hydro massage, LED lighting and a choice of colours.

Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools are also incredibly accommodating and safe for children to use making them an ideal swimming pool choice for families. Featuring low level safety ledges to provide peace of mind whilst the kids play in the pool, Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools also feature variable depths (Marina model only) so that children can play comfortably in the shallow end of the pool.

Installing a Skymirror Swimming Pool

First things first - give us a call and we'll go through it with you! 0151 334 0222 - subject to everything being ok the basics are as follows; 

You will need builders to dig the hole! The Skymirror One Piece In ground Swimming Pool is ordered and is usually available for delivery anywhere between 10 days to 4 weeks.  The pool arrives on the agreed day by lorry with integrated crane and your Skymirror One Piece DIY Pool is then lifted and dropped into the hole your builders will have dug.  The pool is levelled off, pipe work put in place, back filled and finished off. 

Prior to this we can arrange for a Skymirror representative to visit the site for an inspection to make sure all is ok - one of the most important factors to consider, for instance, is access for the lorry to reach the designated place for the pool.

Planning Permission

Planning permission in most cases is not an issue, however give us a call and we'll be glad to advise 0151 334 0222.

Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools features

  • Low level safety ledges
  • Curved large tread staircases with anti-slip surfaces
  • Wide seating areas
  • Constructed using double composite vinylester (which protects against osmosis and ensures longevity to your pool)
  • High quality honeycomb insulation layer for dramatic heat loss reduction

Skymirror One Piece In Ground DIY Swimming Pools are available as three different models: Delta, Golf & Marina.

Skymirror Delta

  • Depth: Water 1.25m & Shell 1.50m
  • Lounger chair: Air bubbler option
  • Bench seating area
  • Safety ledges at 50mm and 900mm deep
  • Anti-slip on all ledges

Skymirror Delta 2014 Prices (exclude VAT) from time to time we have offers on these pools!

  • 7.5m x 3.4m x 1.25m £11,614
  • 7.5m x 3.4m x 1.5m £12,252
  • 9.5m x 3.8m x 1.5m £14,317

With a modern design perfect for swimming enthusiasts, the Delta features slick straight lines that won't infringe on the space of your garden. Add the hydro-massage feature to the integrated lounger seat of the Delta pool and you've got a chic, sporty design also ideal for luxurious relaxation.


 

 Colour options:

All Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pools come supplied with

  • 1 x skimmer
  • 1 x UW light, transformer & deck box
  • 1 x returns
  • 1 x low level suctions
  • 1 x vac point
  • 1 x auto top up

Skymirror One Piece In Ground Swimming Pool Warranty

  • 15 years for integrity of pool
  • 2 years for surface coating
  • 1 year for fitting

Product Description:
Certikin Euroswim Swimming Pool Pump (Powered by DAB)

The Certikin DAB Powered Euroswim Swimming Pool Pump is a highly efficient self-priming centrifugal pump developed for the circulation and filtration of water in domestic and residential swimming pools.

Featuring a completely watertight motor, a built in large capacity pre-filter and reliable operations which run peacefully quiet, the Certikin Euroswim DAB Powered Swimming Pool Pump is also suitable for special applications requiring the handling of aggressive liquids (i.e. agriculture, industry and fish farms).

Certikin Euroswim DAB Powered Swimming Pool Pump features

  • Self-priming centrifugal electric pumps
  • Continuous duty asynchronous motor with electrophoresis treatment
  • Completely watertight motor
  • Pump body in reinforced technopolymer
  • Mechanical seal in carbon, aluminium, NBR and AISI 316 stainless steel
  • Motor cooling ensured by design of fan guard
  • 2" suction and delivery

Advantages of the Certikin Euroswim Swimming Pool Pump

  • Complete range for flow rates up to 42 m3/h
  • Resistant also in aggressive environments
  • Less heat dispersion

Benefits of the Certikin Euroswim Swimming Pool Pump

  • High performance and efficiency
  • Reliable, silent and resistant
  • Long life

Product Name: Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Caravan Roof Light
Product Description:
Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Caravan Roof Light

A tough build for harsh conditions

Built from a robust and weather proof ASA developed especially for caravans, the Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Roof Light features a large opening which accommodates for plenty of light and optimal ventilation. The Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Caravan Roof Light also features a double glazed acrylic panel which is easily opened via the metal bar handle whilst the pane is held open by pneumatic stays for your comfort.

Lockable when the weather gets bad

To protect your caravan from the elements the Seitz Heki 2 Roof Light can also be locked into the bad weather setting to protect against wind and stop rain from entering your Caravan.

Also available: The Deluxe model of the Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Caravan Roof Light

The Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Deluxe Caravan Roof Light benefits from all these same features but with the sparkling addition of 4 integrated lights and improved thermal insulation thanks to a Duette Honeycomb / hollow chamber construction.  Please use the options set at the top of the page to pick your choice between either the original or deluxe model of Dometic Seitz Heki 2 prior to checkout!

Please note - both the standard and deluxe versions of the Heki 2 feature fixed ventilation.

Dometic Seitz Heki 2 Caravan Roof Light

  • The large opening of approx. 780 x 530 mm allows plenty of light and also optimal ventilation
  • Easy installation along or across the Caravan roof (installation requires a flat surface area of 1080 x 780 mm)
  • Roller fly net and blind mounted to the inner frame which can be adjusted independently or combined
  • 25-32mm Standard (32-60mm With an additional installation Kit)
  • Inner frame with blackout and fly screen (can be adjusted separately)
  • Frame colour: cream white (RAL 9001)

Seitz Heki 2 Deluxe Caravan Roof Light features

  • Inner aluminium lining which absorbs up to 99% of harmful UV rays
  • 4 integrated 5 Watt bulbs for soft, subdued lighting
  • Precision produced with Duette honeycomb material
  • Blind and fly net mounted to the inner frame (can be operated together or independently, by means of two fixing bars)New fixing bars specially developed to match the colours of the inner frame
  • 25-32mm Standard (32-60mm With an additional installation Kit)
  • Frame colour: cream white (RAL 9001)

 The Heki 2 is supplied with a fixing kit for a standard roof thickness of 25-32 mm

Product Name: Dometic FreshJet FJX7 3000 Motorhome Inverter Air Conditioner
Product Description:
Dometic FreshJet FJX7 3000 Motorhome and Caravan Air Conditioner

Powerful and Reliable Air Conditioning with a Sleek Design

Manage the temperature on your next adventure with the Dometic Freshjet FJX7 3000 Air Conditioner, a professional class Air Conditioner produced by Dometic. The Air Con Unit comes fitted with the latest speed-controlled inverter compressor and heat pump technology. This will allow you to quickly, quietly and efficiently cool or heat your caravan, motorhome or campervan! The Air Conditioner is a roof unit and needs to be fitted to the rooftop. The design is sleek, elegant and minimalistic with an LED light curve to complement your caravan / motorhome's aesthetics and provide an element of ambiance at night. Despite its impressive 2516W of cooling power, the FreshJet 3000 maintains a quiet noise profile due to the patented dual-cylinder inverter, which balances the system to provide quiet and efficient operation. The efficiency of the unit means it has a very low starting current, allowing smooth operation even on campsites with low electrical protection.

Modern Motorhome Air Conditioning Powered by Smart Technology

The Dometic Freshjet FJX7 3000 Rooftop Air Conditioner is equipped with Smart connectivity features, which will allow users to control the heating through a range of convenient touchpoints, such as the smart phone app, a remote control or the built-in touch screen interface. The compressor does not work via traditional method of an On/Off switch, but via Integrated Smart Technology. The compressor adapts automatically to environmental demands, helping to save both time from adjusting the temperature and energy from turning the device on and off throughout the day. The air conditioner is the perfect addition to help modify any caravan or motorhome into a mobile smart mobile-home! The integrated CleanAir system helps to maintain Air Quality within a Caravan or Motorhome by keeping the air fresh and clear, and working to remove allergens, bacteria and mould. You can switch between heating and cooling, set a desired temperature, dehumidify, ventilate, set a desired temperature - or simply activate auto mode. For the winter months, the unit comes equipped with a mighty 3107W of heating power to keep you and your loved ones warm. The unit also features integrated bright LED lighting, which can be activated via the remote control.

Sleek and Compact Caravan Air Conditioning

The Dometic FreshJet FJX7 3000 Roof Air Conditioner is one of the most lightweight and ultra-compact motorhome / caravan air conditioners in all of Europe. It is ideal for motorhomes or caravans up to 7m in length, and all campervans models because of it's small design and powerful features. The sleep mode feature reduces fan speed by 80%, creating a peaceful, temperature-controlled environment to enjoy late nights in your campervan.

Dometic Freshjet  FJX7 3000 Motorhome Roof Air Conditioner - Features:

  • The flagship motorhome & caravan air conditioner in the Dometic range
  • Cooling and Heating Functionality
  • Superior Air Regulation Technology - motorhomes, caravans or campervans can be cooled at a rapid pace.
  • Superior Energy Efficiency - Advanced compressor and Heat Pump technology reduce general power consumption of the device
  • Sleep mode - Fan speed reduces by 80% to minimise noise when in operation
  • Advanced Soft Start Function - quiet and gentle air conditioner start-up
  • Whisper-quiet operation - with its variable dual-cylinder compressor speed, the FJX7 operates silently while maintaining the desired temperature
  • Remote control included as standard
  • Dometic Climate App - utilise the modern functionalities by controlling your roof air conditioner from the convenience of your smartphone
  • Touchscreen functionalities for quick-fix temperature control
  • Clean Air Purify Technology - effectively reduces bacteria, odours and other pollutants to keep your motorhome, caravan or campervan smelling fresh and clean.
  • Outlet fans are vertically adjustable, allowing for individual airflow regulation if desired
  • Optimised Airflow - new low-profile air distribution box with powerful front and back airflow
  • Low-key and compact design makes the Air conditioner a stealthy upgrade to your campervan or motorhome
  • Built-in LEDs for a gentle ambient light
  • Re-usable dust filter, easy for cleaning
  • Exclusive premium design - aerodynamically shaped rooftop with eye catching LED light curve

Dometic FreshJet 3000 Caravan & Motorhome Air Conditioner - Specifications:

  • Rapid cooling (2516 watts)
  • Powerful heating function (3107 watts)
  • Removes excess humidity from air
  • Includes ventilation mode, ideal for cooking

Product Name: CS Evolution CSE 240 Caravan Solar Charge Regulator
Product Description:
CS Evolution CSE 240 Caravan Solar Charge Regulator

The CS Evolution CSE 240 Solar Charge Regulator uses the latest technology to ensure for maximum efficiency and is capable of running one or two solar panels through it (totalling 240w).

Featuring a microprocessor controlled MOSFET, the CS Evolution CSE 240 Solar Charge Regulator uses only 0.05 Amp of power to operate thanks to its ultra intelligent software.

The CS Evolution CSE 240 Solar Charge Regulator uses a series of LEDs to indicate system status, including: Charge, end of charge (battery OK), fuse failure alarm (fuse), alarm connection (rev. polarity).

Product Description:
CS Evolution CSE 230 Caravan & Motorhome Solar Regulator

Similar to the CSE 240 regulator but without the ability to charge the engine battery of your caravan or motorhome, the CS Evolution CSE 230 Caravan & Motorhome Solar Regulator is however still able to charge batteries at the rate of 20A as well as regulate up to 230w of power (i.e. 2 x 115w panels)

The CS Evolution CSE 230 Caravan & Motorhome Solar Regulator can charge either lead acid or gel batteries by using the selector switch accordingly and also uses the same microprocessor technology as the CSE 240 Regulator (i.e. only uses 0.05 Amp of power in order to charge the batteries!)

Product Name: Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Caravan Porch Awning
Product Description:
Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Caravan Awning 

Designed for short stays and touring holidays, the Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Caravan Porch Awning is the ultimate quick and easy caravan porch awning, providing durability, convenience and spacious comfort alongside a speedy, hassle free installation.

How does the Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Awning work?

In fact, the Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Caravan Porch Awning only requires a few pump strokes in order to inflate each tube (2.5 bar) and get the inflatable awning taking shape, erected and ready for use! 

Is a Eurovent Luna AirCamp Inflatable Awning just as resistant as a traditional frame awning?

The inflatable frame of the Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Caravan Porch Awning is made of Thermo polyurethane (TPU), renowned for its exceptional resistance against wear and tear and its air permeability.

Reinforced sleeves further increase a high level of protection against puncturing as well as storm and wind resistance, with each arch inflated independently so they can also be easily replaced, making the Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Awning equal to traditional awning frame awnings in terms of strength and endurance!

Eurovent Luna AirCamp 280 Inflatable Caravan Awning features

  • Taped seams
  • Rear bumper pads
  • Draught skirt included
  • Window blinds
  • Secondary mesh side doors
  • Supplied complete with pegs and instructions
  • Mosquito net on front and on door panels

Why Choose an AGM Deep cycle Battery?

 

Pros

Cons
AGM
  • Fast Recharge Time
  • Long Life (7-10 Years)
  • Sealed Unit
  • Can be Mounted anyway (excluding inverted)
  • Excellent life with irregular charging
  • Excells with High Burst Amp requirements (eg fridges, A/C)
  • slow discharge rate
  • High Price (compared to lead acid)
  • Must be stored in charged condition
GEL
  • Long Life (12 year)
  • Sealed Unit
  • Can be Mounted anyway (excluding inverted)
  • Works in Higher ambient tempratures
  • minimal discharge rate
  • Most Expensive
  • sensitive to improper recharge cycle
  • Must be stored in charged condition
Lead Acid
  • Cheap
  • Short Life (3-5 Years)
  • Possible Leaks
  • Must be installed upright
  • Fastest Discharge Rate
  • Less Effective in cold conditions

Product Name: Whale Aquasource Water Filter 12mm Quick Connect
Product Description:
Whale Aquasource Water Filter 12mm Quick Connect

Featuring silverised carbon filters designed to remove unpleasant tastes and smells from your water supply, the Whale Aquasource Water Filter 12mm Quick Connect comes with clips for a simple installation.

The Whale Aquasource Water Filter 12mm Quick Connect is maintenance free and can be mounted either vertically or horizontally and installed in freshwater plumbing pipework (usually under the sink!).

How to drain the Whale Aquasource Water Filter for winterisation

  • Open all taps in the caravan
  • Open the drain valve
  • Tilt caravan so drain plug is lowest
  • Let the water run out of drain valve

Whale Aquasource Water Filter 12mm Quick Connect features

  • Lasts one full season (or 4500 litres)
  • Maximum Pressure 4 bar (60 psi)
  • Suitable for 12mm pipework

Please note: This is not a bacterial filter.

Whale Aquasmart Water Filter

Product Name: Astral H5 Duo Automatic Electronic Swimming Pool Cleaner
Product Description:
Astral H5 Duo Automatic Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner

Enjoy a Cleaner Pool with the new H5DUO Suction Pool Cleaner

H5 Duo is a leading model of automatic robotic swimming pool cleaners. With cutting-edge technology and a contemporary design which makes the H5 Duo the top-of-the-range cleaner for private pools.

The H5 Duo automatic swimming pool cleaning has a new ultrafine 3D filter as standard providing a high quality cleaning finish, adjustable suction nozzles and PVA brushing providing a better quality grip for cleaning coverage on the bottom and walls of the swimming pool. The H5 Duo automatic swimming pool cleaner comes with a LED indicator which shows when the filter is full and are easily accessible from the top of the H5 Duo cleaner as well as windows to see the level of debris.

Advantages of a single platform and a block comprising 2 motors and 1 filtration pump:

• Improved power transmission.
• More effective vibration cleaning brush.
• Lasts longer: no drive belts required and enhanced motor seals.
• Enhanced features: double traction motor + Gyro system.
• Easy for customers to repair: 4 screws to replace the motor block and direct access to gears and bearings.

Product Name: Astral H7 Duo Robotic Swimming Pool Electronic Cleaner
Product Description:
Astral H7 Duo Robotic Swimming Pool Cleaner

Enjoy double the cleaning power for a dirt free swimming pool with the Astral H7 Duo Cleaner!

The Astral H7 Duo Robotic Swimming Pool Cleaner shares many of the same exceptional features and technology as the supreme H5 but with the addition of a few extra innovations. Featuring an extended cable length, pre programmed pool shape, advanced swivel system and 2 x 24v DC Drive Motor, the Astral H7 Duo Robotic Swimming Pool Cleaner is built to accommodate for larger sized domestic swimming pools of up to 18m in length.

For further ease of use and versatility, the Astral H7 Duo Robotic Swimming Pool Cleaner also comes with top access filters (with LED indicator to signify when the filter is full) as well as 2 suction nozzles which are height adjustable to suit any swimming pool.

Astral H7 Duo Robotic Swimming Pool Cleaner key features

  • Pre-programmed pool shape
  • Advanced swivel shape
  • Longer cable length     
  • 2 x 24v DC Drive motor
  • Direct, easy access to the filter
  • Fast-moving brush for effective cleaning
  • Electronic swivel system
  • Aquasmart technology to calculate the smartest route of your swimming pool
  • An LED indicator which lights up when the filter is full
  • Thoroughly cleans walls, floor and water line of swimming pool

Product Name: Waeco Perfect Control MPC01 Battery Management System
Product Description:
Waeco Perfect Control MPC01 Battery Management System

An intelligent battery management system and battery sensor, the Waeco Perfect Control MPC01 provides an exact analysis of the charge status of your battery.

A complimentary bit of kit for the Waeco Perfect Charge battery chargers, the Waeco Perfect Control MPC01 Battery Management System features an easy to use operating panel which provides straight forward monitoring information regarding the status of the connected batteries and battery charger as well as their voltage, current, capacity and remaining operating time.

Waeco Perfect Control MPC01 Battery Management System features:

  • Input voltage: 8 - 30 volts
  • Current consumption: 150 mA in display mode, 10mA in standby mode
  • CIS bus and RS232 interface
  • Suitable for 3 additional battery sensors to be connected
  • Display dimensions: (W x H x D) 130 x 115 x 06mm
  • Installation frame dimension: (W x H x D) 150 x 136 x 16mm

Product Name: Dometic Waeco Coolmatic CD30 Under Bench Drawer Fridge
Product Description:
Dometic Waeco Coolmatic CD 30 Under Bench Drawer Fridge

Designed to be built into your caravan or motorhome for a space efficient refrigeration solution, the Waeco Coolmatic CD 30 Under Bench Drawer Fridge provides convenient access and high performance cooling.

Built from high quality insulating material to help reduce power consumption, the Waeco Coolmatic CD 30 Under Bench Drawer Fridge also features a safe locking mechanism (with unlocking and opening achieved via a simple, single movement) and roller bearing slides for a smooth, side action drawer which is easy to open.

The Waeco Coolmatic CD 30 Under Bench Drawer Fridge can be run from 12v and 24v DC and has a 30 litre capacity. The cooling unit can be fitted to the side of the Waeco Coolmatic CD 30 Drawer Fridge (left/right), or up to 1.5 metres away.

Dometic Waeco Coolmatic CD 30 Under Bench Drawer Fridge features

  • Fully hermetic Danfoss BD35F compressor with integrated control electronics
  • Low-voltage protection for starter battery
  • Electronic fuse/automatic reverse pole protection
  • Dynamically ventilated wire tube condenser
  • Aluminium rollbond evaporator
  • Heat dissipation to the outside with brushless wear-free fan
  • Convenient access with easy-pull drawer fridge running on roller bearing slides
  • Temperature regulation with continuously variable thermostat
  • Unlocking and opening with a single movement
  • Safe locking mechanism

Waeco Coolmatic CR65S Compressor Stainless Steel Fridge

A 64 litre CR-Series of Waeco Fridges featuring a stylish stainless steel front

With all the same exceptional features, technology and dimensions of the standard Waeco CR65, the Waeco CR65S Compressor Fridge comes with the attractive addition of a stunning stainless steel finish.

Waeco Coolmatic CR65S Compressor Stainless Steel Fridge features:

Spinflo Cara Caravan & Motorhome Cooker

With it’s compact design, the Spinflo Cara Cooker is an incredibly lightweight yet robust oven for caravans and motorhomes with a stylish design. 

Thermostatically controlled with flame failure device, the Spinflo Cara Caravan and Motorhome Cooker comes with fitting instructions supplied.

Spinflo Cara Caravan and Motorhome Cooker features

  • Exterior dimensions: 420 x 483 x 475mm (H x W x D)
  • Fitting aperture dimensions: 445 x 433 x 428mm (H x W x D)
  • Capacity: 34 litres
  • Weight: 11kg
  • Gas Connection: 8mm (cooper, propane or butane)
